After payment of the Purchase Money Mortgage balance to Habitat for Humanity, there shall be paid to the Grantee (Seller) an amount equal to the then remaining sale proceeds multiplied by a percentage (%) factor equal to the number of complete years (or part of a year) the Grantee (Seller) has made payments on the Purchase Money Mortgage times (x) 5% per year or 1/20th of this remainder; and <laysep@@##$$> c.
